<br>
Yeah Defense is a slow skill to raise, besides kick its definatly my slowest for me. It seems to raise most when in a multiple badguy combat, sometimes if im with a druid friend and they snare the mob ill get another and let it beat on me while i finish the other mob, seems defense has a higher chance of raising then but maybe thats just me<br>
<br>
A Langseax is a good weapon to keep 1hs skill up but having low dam and delay is only good if you aint gonna be diein anytime soon... generaly the weapon wont matter too much, id say only get a low dam low delay weapon when youre tryin to raise a skill that youre way behind in, otherwise stick to the high damage low delay concept (imo).<br>
<br>
Goodluck to ya<br>
<br>
Brewtus<br>
